---
title: Chocolate Zucchini Bread Serves 2 | with Chocolate Chips
description: Sweet and savoury zucchini bread is sure to satisfy all of your dessert cravings. Zucchini keeps the cake nice and moist, while cocoa powder and chocolate combine for a decadent bite!
